  {
    num: "962"
    title: "Recipe"
    description: "A cooking recipe with ingredients and steps."
    shapeIndex: 3
    mamlText: "{\n  title: \"Lasagne\"\n  servings: 2\n  prep_time: \"17 minutes\"\n  cook_time: \"72 minutes\"\n\n  # Ingredients\n  ingredients: [\n    \"2 pieces lobster\"\n    \"3 cups purple rice\"\n    \"1 tbsp tempeh\"\n  ]\n\n  # Instructions\n  steps: [\n    \"A heartwarming Armenian soup, featuring fresh nuts and an aromatic blend of traditional spices.\"\n    \"A slow-roasted Little Shearwater with a tangy, tangy exterior. Stuffed with strawberry and covered in blood orange sauce. Sides with potatoes puree and wild sun dried tomatoes.\"\n    \"A heartwarming Nepalese soup, featuring fresh mastic and an aromatic blend of traditional spices.\"\n    \"A robust fresh stew featuring Karnataka flavors, loaded with fresh meat, tangy vegetables, and a golden, spicy broth.\"\n    \"A delightful tart combining golden french eschallots and sweet kiwi fruit, set in a buttery pastry shell and finished with a hint of lemon pepper.\"\n    \"A special mint green bamboo shoots from Jersey. To support the strong flavor it is sided with a tablespoon of five spice.\"\n  ]\n\n  nutrition: {\n    calories: 619\n    protein: \"5g\"\n    carbs: \"76g\"\n    fat: \"29g\"\n  }\n}"
  }
  {
    num: "963"
    title: "Recipe"
    description: "A cooking recipe with ingredients and steps."
    shapeIndex: 3
    mamlText: "{\n  title: \"Fresh Mandarin And Brussels Sprouts Salad\"\n  servings: 8\n  prep_time: \"57 minutes\"\n  cook_time: \"101 minutes\"\n\n  # Ingredients\n  ingredients: [\n    \"4 pieces lychees\"\n    \"4 tsp farmed prawns\"\n    \"1 tsp sprouts\"\n  ]\n\n  # Instructions\n  steps: [\n    \"An exquisite goose roast, infused with the essence of nashi pear, slow-roasted to bring out its natural flavors and served with a side of creamy chinese cabbage\"\n    \"A moist lettuce creation, seasoned with anise star and anise, showcasing the best of plant-based cuisine.\"\n    \"Baked tamari-stuffed salmon, seasoned with chillies and crispy herbs, accompanied by roasted rhubarb medley.\"\n    \"Crispy fried quail bites, seasoned with fennel seed and served with a tangy peach dipping sauce.\"\n    \"A special white pineapple from Cameroon. To support the strong flavor it is sided with a tablespoon of balti stir fry mix.\"\n  ]\n\n  nutrition: {\n    calories: 514\n    protein: \"24g\"\n    carbs: \"34g\"\n    fat: \"5g\"\n  }\n}"
  }
  {
    num: "964"
    title: "Resume"
