    description: "Test runner configuration with coverage settings."
    shapeIndex: 3
    mamlText: "{\n  runner: \"jest\"\n  root: \"./src/__tests__\"\n  include: [\n    \"**/*.test.ts\"\n    \"**/*.spec.ts\"\n  ]\n  exclude: [\n    \"node_modules\"\n    \"dist\"\n    \"**/*.e2e.ts\"\n  ]\n\n  # Coverage\n  coverage: {\n    enabled: true\n    provider: \"istanbul\"\n    thresholds: {\n      lines: 93\n      branches: 70\n      functions: 82\n    }\n    reporter: [\n      \"text\"\n      \"lcov\"\n      \"html\"\n    ]\n  }\n  globals: true\n  timeout: 27136 # ms\n}"
