    title: "Queue Config"
    description: "Message queue and worker configuration."
    shapeIndex: 1
    mamlText: "{\n  broker: \"kafka\"\n  connection: {\n    host: \"localhost\"\n    port: 9092\n    vhost: \"/production\"\n  }\n\n  # Queue definitions\n  queues: {\n    default: {\n      concurrency: 4\n      retry: 2\n      timeout: 55508 # ms\n    }\n\n    priority: {\n      concurrency: 7\n      retry: 10\n      timeout: 1785 # ms\n    }\n  }\n\n  dead_letter: {\n    enabled: true\n    max_retries: 9\n    queue: \"dead-letter\"\n  }\n}"
