    description: "A cooking recipe with ingredients and steps."
    shapeIndex: 3
    mamlText: "{\n  title: \"Mustard-rubbed Chicken Salad\"\n  servings: 6\n  prep_time: \"39 minutes\"\n  cook_time: \"50 minutes\"\n\n  # Ingredients\n  ingredients: [\n    \"1 tbsp arborio rice\"\n    \"4 tbsp dark chocolate\"\n    \"2 pieces mung beans\"\n    \"3 lbs dried chinese broccoli\"\n  ]\n\n  # Instructions\n  steps: [\n    \"A special olive yogurt from Bangladesh. To support the strong flavor it is sided with a tablespoon of oregano.\"\n    \"Tender goose skewers, glazed with a sweet and tangy tomato sauce, served over a bed of fragrant jasmine rice.\"\n    \"A special orchid cavalo from Mongolia. To support the strong flavor it is sided with a tablespoon of allspice.\"\n    \"Tenderly braised salmon in a rich poudre de colombo and asian greens sauce, served with a side of creamy broccolini.\"\n    \"A robust savory stew featuring Soviet flavors, loaded with spicy meat, fresh vegetables, and a zesty, tender broth.\"\n    \"A golden broccolini creation, seasoned with lavender and korma, showcasing the best of plant-based cuisine.\"\n  ]\n\n  nutrition: {\n    calories: 754\n    protein: \"47g\"\n    carbs: \"97g\"\n    fat: \"39g\"\n  }\n}"
  }
